#. Key:	722AD2F44B367F2476680FB521EA07EA
msgctxt ",722AD2F44B367F2476680FB521EA07EA"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Yeah, down by the lake there is a little shed with a fishing rod and everything you need to fish really</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Sí, junto al lago hay una pequeña caseta con una caña y todo lo que necesitas para pescar, básicamente</>"

#. Key:	2B516C0B4E644E6C3A7052B83C0A3C2E
msgctxt ",2B516C0B4E644E6C3A7052B83C0A3C2E"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>That sounds interesting, I might have to check that out.</>"
