msgctxt ",ED84833F4CEC9F876E97A2AC4035F4E2"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Hey everyone! I just got a radio in about some hiker who didn't find his way out of the park. If you see him just help him on his way alright? I prefer not hearing about this in the news later.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>¡Hola a todos! Acabo de recibir un aviso por radio sobre un excursionista que no encontró la salida del parque. Si lo ven, ayúdenlo a seguir su camino, ¿vale? Preferiría no oír esto luego en las noticias.</>"

#. Key:	KailynE80B92419BCACAC6405CA5DB127F7E
msgctxt ",KailynE80B92419BCACAC6405CA5DB127F7E"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Yes, what is it?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Sí, ¿qué pasa?</>"

#. Key:	56F0C0CF4133DF9182B91F8B1B29C288
msgctxt ",56F0C0CF4133DF9182B91F8B1B29C288"
msgid "<Kailyn>???: </><Speech>You know those Aquilegia formosas down by the creek. I really thought they wouldn't make it but with yesterday's rain I think they might just pull through.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>???: </><Speech>¿Sabes esas Aquilegia formosas junto al arroyo? De verdad pensé que no iban a sobrevivir, pero con la lluvia de ayer creo que quizá salgan adelante.</>"

#. Key:	F707F95043B160BDD0AF969E2B782300
msgctxt ",F707F95043B160BDD0AF969E2B782300"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Alright, that's great. Why are telling me this?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Vale, eso está genial. ¿Por qué me cuentas esto?</>"

#. Key:	168C7615423C60729BCE23982BB59526
msgctxt ",168C7615423C60729BCE23982BB59526"
msgid "<Kailyn>???: </><Speech>Well...I just thought I'd tell you, it's not like there are many people to speak with out here.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>???: </><Speech>Bueno... solo pensé en contártelo, no es que haya mucha gente con quien hablar aquí.</>"

#. Key:	A43423084894EB3BDEEE778EAE46514A
msgctxt ",A43423084894EB3BDEEE778EAE46514A"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Kailyn, only contact me if there is an emergency or when you're reporting. You know how busy I am.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Kailyn, contáctame solo si hay una emergencia o cuando estés reportando. Sabes lo ocupado que estoy.</>"

#. Key:	A29391ED42745D6E0A4003AE71A4395B
msgctxt ",A29391ED42745D6E0A4003AE71A4395B"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>(Grunt)</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>(Gruñido)</>"

#. Key:	AEED0DCD453A595C652DCF88409E31D4
msgctxt ",AEED0DCD453A595C652DCF88409E31D4"
msgid "<Kailyn>???: </><Speech>Yeah.. I'm sure you're real busy.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>???: </><Speech>Sí... seguro que estás muy ocupado.</>"

#. Key:	8CE603804E39E09E8C31F5936A9369BF
msgctxt ",8CE603804E39E09E8C31F5936A9369BF"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Alright, I'm gonna head off for the night. Park's all yours</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Bueno, me voy por esta noche. El parque es todo tuyo</>"

#. Key:	0A7D7A7B41D82E83EED883ACF7F04C82
msgctxt ",0A7D7A7B41D82E83EED883ACF7F04C82"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Alright listen up everybody! Rick here..I'm gonna have to head out for a week or so, so I will be unavailable for the time being.  Family emergency, you know how it is. If you need something just reach out to most experienced fire lookout in your sector, they'll know what to do. And if you can't make it a week without me, who did we even hire?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>¡Muy bien, escuchen todos! Aquí Rick... voy a tener que irme una semana o así, así que no estaré disponible por el momento. Emergencia familiar, ya saben cómo es. Si necesitan algo, contacten con el vigilante de incendios más experimentado de su sector, sabrá qué hacer. Y si no pueden aguantar una semana sin mí, ¿a quién demonios contratamos?</>"

#. Key:	1329620142BB94BDB8CF0DA339866481
msgctxt ",1329620142BB94BDB8CF0DA339866481"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>You scared me shit out of me.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Me diste un susto de muerte.</>"

